Class AbstractEllipse

  • java.lang.Object
    • pythagoras.f.RectangularShape
      • pythagoras.f.AbstractEllipse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, IEllipse, IRectangularShape, IShape
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ellipse

    public abstract class AbstractEllipse
extends RectangularShape
implements IEllipse
    Provides most of the implementation of IEllipse, obtaining the framing rectangle from the derived class.
